{"tid":2426128,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–微生物大戰","createTime":"2021-02-27T22:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T00:44:18.000Z","uid":38861,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb88c5e3be3b3308a82fdf2bf01f1184151faae","tid":2426128,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T22:32:56.000Z","msg":"除人類外，微生物們亦會串通一起，把共同敵人一網打盡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeDLV0n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeDLV0n.png&h=572440ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）捕食性真菌(Zoophagus insidians)會發展出網狀的菌絲體(Mycelium)，這些菌絲體的尖端有著大大小小的微孔，給予細菌們寄居的空間。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6iss9kq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6iss9kq.png&h=ec6f2301&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）菌絲體上的尖端會扣著環境中的輪蟲，使牠們動彈不能。<br />\n左圖紅色區域為輪蟲身上的油脂，如右圖所見，這些油脂會經由捕食性真菌的菌絲體所吸取。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yFqV0t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yFqV0t.png&h=421147ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而寄居在菌絲體上尖端的細菌們，亦會乘機享用輪蟲身上的各種營養。<br />\n<br />\n這種種的一切發生在一滴水滴裡頭，利用顯微鏡觀察才能見到。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3s22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=e44a52e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3s22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=a04e1399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.mdpi.com/1422-0067/22/4/2178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F1422-0067%2F22%2F4%2F2178&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3s22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=e2561a1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mdpi.com/1422-0067/22/4/2178</a>"},{"pid":"79be65adee10860b3234f6673628c91a1ac79e0e","tid":2426128,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"輪蟲好慘豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7de7b32b773d3e82e2f44df61d02d233791974","tid":2426128,"uid":155238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"菇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最憎食"},{"pid":"9af152d65209e5f26a57ffebb7bc48f5001ceede","tid":2426128,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e308797b6a08abf7c75176a9ebf855571d28d7d3","tid":2426128,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79be65adee10860b3234f6673628c91a1ac79e0e","tid":2426128,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"輪蟲好慘豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=